OL,3,CFormer church curate 'exploited his
OL,4,Crole' to abuse boys
OL,6,FA former church curate from Bideford
OL,7,Fwho exploited his role to sexually
OL,8,Fabuse two boys has been handed a 11-
OL,9,Fyear prison sentence.
OL,11,FJulian Wheeler, 75, of Mount Raleigh
OL,12,FAvenue was found guilty of 13 child
OL,13,Fsexual abuse offences at Exeter Crown
OL,14,FCourt following a seven-day trial.
OL,16,FAt the time of the offending, Mr
OL,17,FWheeler was working as a curate in a
OL,18,Fchurch, a role he held from 1975 until
OL,19,F2003.
