OL,6,FThe court heard how the abuse against
OL,7,Fthe first victim began in the 1980s
OL,8,Fwith Wheeler befriending the boy and
OL,9,Fhis family often visiting the family
OL,10,Fhome.
OL,12,FOn numerous occasions, he would attend
OL,13,Fthe address and sexually abuse the boy
OL,14,Fover a four-year period.
OL,16,FWheeler began to abuse the second
OL,17,Fvictim in the 1990s, again after
OL,18,Fbefriending the victim.
