OL,3,CFormer church curate 'exploited his
OL,4,Crole' to abuse boys
OL,6,FHe often helped the boy with his
OL,7,Fhomework before exploiting this
OL,8,Ffriendship and subjecting the victim
OL,9,Fto years of sexual abuse.
OL,11,FIn 2017, the first victim came forward
OL,12,Fto police about the abuse they
OL,13,Fsuffered at the hands of Wheeler.
OL,15,FOfficers launched an investigation and
OL,16,Fcontacted the other victim who had
OL,17,Fpreviously reported similar offences
OL,18,Fagainst Wheeler.
