OL,3,CFormer church curate 'exploited his
OL,4,Crole' to abuse boys
OL,6,FDetective Inspector Elaine Westerman
OL,7,Fsaid: "This man was in a position of
OL,8,Ftrust. He used his role as a church
OL,9,Fcurate to gain access to vulnerable
OL,10,Fboys which he went on to abuse.
OL,12,F"I am extremely grateful to both of
OL,13,Fthe victims for supporting the
OL,14,Finvestigation. We welcome the outcome
OL,15,Ftoday and hope that they can find
OL,16,Fcomfort in justice being served.
