OL,6,F"I truly hope that this gives other
OL,7,Fvictims the confidence to come forward
OL,8,Fto report sexual offences, no matter
OL,9,Fhow long ago they may have happened.
OL,10,FWe will work with you and support you
OL,11,Fwhile we seek the justice you deserve."
OL,13,FDistrict Crown Prosecutor, Suzie
OL,14,FButler said: "We are very pleased that
OL,15,Fwe were able to deliver justice for
OL,16,Fthe victims in this case and we
OL,17,Facknowledge the immense courage and
OL,18,Fbravery they showed in coming forward
OL,19,Fand in supporting the prosecution.
